'''''Omo Ghetto''''' (English translation: '''''Child of the Ghetto)''''' ni filimi yasohotse 2010 muri [[Nigeria]]  iyoborwa na Abiodun Olarenwaju, Star Funke Akindele, Rasheli Oniga, Taiwo Hassan, Yinka Quadri na Eniola Badmus <ref>https://ng.opera.news/tags/abiodun-olanrewaju</ref>.<ref>https://spurplayafrica.com/entertainment-%26-culture/f/omo-ghetto-smashes-at-the-cinemas-and-here-is-why</ref> 

== Umugambi ==
Filime ishingiye ku ngeso mbi za societe nitsinda ryiganjemo abagore.<ref>https://www.insidenolly.ng/abiodun-olanrewaju-abbey-lanre/</ref>

== Kwakira ==
Olusegun Michael wo muri ''[[Gana]] ya none'' yashimye uwo mugambi, gukina, insanganyamatsiko no gusobanura uruhare muri iyi filime, avuga ko ari filime "idakora, ishimishije kandi ihishura"<ref>https://www.newtelegraphng.com/i-almost-passed-out-filming-omo-ghetto-the-saga-funke-akindele/</ref>.  Muri 2017, Azeezat Kareem wo mu kinyamakuru Encomium Magazine yashyize ahagaragara ''Omo Ghetto'' nka imwe muri filime ebyiri zatumye Eniola Badmus amenyekana cyane mu nganda za firime zo muri [[Nijeriya]]<ref>https://www.bellanaija.com/2020/12/funke-akindele-bello-omo-ghetto/</ref>.  Yashyizwe kandi muri Legit.ng film eshanu "zitazibagirana" za Funke Akindele <ref>https://thenet.ng/how-funke-akindele-made-eniola-badmus-a-star/</ref>. 

